org.apache.ignite.igfs.mapreduce.records

Class IgfsByteDelimiterRecordResolver

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.ignite.igfs.mapreduce.records.IgfsByteDelimiterRecordResolver
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Externalizable, Serializable, IgfsRecordResolver
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    IgfsNewLineRecordResolver, IgfsStringDelimiterRecordResolver

    public class IgfsByteDelimiterRecordResolver
extends Object
implements IgfsRecordResolver, Externalizable
    Record resolver which adjusts records based on provided delimiters. Both start position and length are shifted to the right, based on delimiter positions.

    Note that you can use IgfsStringDelimiterRecordResolver if your delimiter is a plain string.

    Serialized Form
